title: Gallery of
desc: Get to know more about the farmers, students, instructors, and activities at West Lampung Coffe School.
info1: Here, you can explore various educational and exciting moments that happen at Coffe School. Each photo and video is presented to bring you closer to the unique coffee-making process, the natural beauty of West Lampung, and the educational tourism experience we offer.
info2: In this gallery, you will find fascinating photos that depict our coffee journey, from mesmerizing coffee plantation tours, coffee cherry picking process
info3: to inspiring coffee workshops. Discover the natural beauty and long-standing coffee traditions of this region.
